    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>African textile material of Ewe origin but adapted and varied by other peoples, woven on a loom in narrow strips to produce strong patterns. A popular cloth, it is traded all around the Niger Delta region.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
